    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just so quiet here. i walk into the kitchen and i forget for a split second that he’s not coming back, and then it hits me all over again. the house feels like a tomb. i don't even recognize myself in the mirror anymore. i feel like i’m just a ghost wandering around a life that doesn't belong to me anymore. everything feels so pointless.",
